@node FAME "WHAT THE HELL IS FAME ?????"

@{u}Some informations about FAME@{uu}

What is FAME, you may ask. FAME is a new BBS-System written by Strider of
Syndicate, which is about 90% compatible to Amiex-Doors, but has also an
own Message-Port to use more than 1000 (!) commands. The whole BBS is 
completly hardware-depend, meaning that the only limit this system has is
your computer-equipment !
The configuration and the control of the BBS is realized with a System-Editor 
(fully Gadtoolsdriven, NO ICONS ANYMORE!), and a very comfortable Server 
(Commodity- & Gadtools-driven).

During the fact that this BBS is currently in Beta-Stage, it's not avail-
able until now, but if you want more informations, contact us and we will 
give you all informations needed.
@endnode

