@node REGVERSION "REGISTERED ENHANCED VERSION OF CD-SERVER"

@{u}Changings to the Registered Version of CD-Server@{uu}

If you want to get support for CD-Server, you have to pay the @{"Registration" LINK COPYRIGHT}
fee. As registered user, you get the following enhancements for CD-Server:

- Zippy Search functions are built-in
- Level-depend Devices/Assigns, useful to let Cosys in your C: for example
- Internal Packfunctions with Size-Limitations
- User-Configurable Dirstyles & other options (like favourite Packer etc.)

and of course all your wishes (if possible of course) you have to this or
to other programs listed @{"HERE" LINK PRGLIST}. So it's your choice to keep the development
of this and other doors...
@endnode
